class Solution {
    public void setZeroes(int[][] matrix) {

        int n = matrix.length;
        int m = matrix[0].length;

        int col0 = 1;

        // Step 1: Mark rows and columns
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {

                if (matrix[i][j] == 0) {

                    // mark the i-th row
                    matrix[i][0] = 0;

                    // mark the j-th column
                    if (j != 0) {
                        matrix[0][j] = 0;
                    } else {
                        col0 = 0;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Step 2: Set elements to 0 based on marks
        for (int i = 1; i < n; i++) {
            for (int j = 1; j < m; j++) {

                if (matrix[i][j] != 0) {

                    // check for row & column marks
                    if (matrix[i][0] == 0 || matrix[0][j] == 0) {
                        matrix[i][j] = 0;
                    }
                }
            }
        }

        // Step 3: Set first row to 0
        if (matrix[0][0] == 0) {
            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {
                matrix[0][j] = 0;
            }
        }

        // Step 4: Set first column to 0
        if (col0 == 0) {
            for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                matrix[i][0] = 0;
            }
        }
    }
}




Step 1: Rows aur Columns ko Mark Karna
Sabse pehle hum matrix ke andar traverse karte hain. Agar hume kisi cell matrix[i][j] == 0 milta hai, toh hum samajh jaate hain ki poori i-th row aur poori j-th col ko 0 karna padega.
Hum iski marking usi matrix ki 1st row aur 1st col mein kar dete hain.
matrix[i][0] = 0; ka matlab hai: "Yeh poori row 0 hogi."
matrix[0][j] = 0; ka matlab hai: "Yeh poora column 0 hoga."
Edge Case (j == 0): Kyunki matrix[0][0] row aur column dono ke liye common hai, isliye pehle column (column 0) ke liye hum ek alag variable col0 ka use karte hain.
Step 2: Inner Matrix ko 0 Set Karna
Ab hum row 1 aur column 1 se start karke (yaani pehli row aur pehle col ko chhodkar) baki poori matrix par loop chalate hain.
Har element matrix[i][j] ke liye hum check karte hain ki kya uski row ka marker (matrix[i][0]) ya uske column ka marker (matrix[0][j]) zero hai?
Agar dono mein se koi bhi zero hai, toh hum us element ko 0 set kar dete hain.
Step 3: Pehli Row (1st Row) ko Zero Karna
Ab baari aati hai un markers ki jinko dekh kar humne baki matrix badli thi.
Agar matrix[0][0] == 0 hai, iska matlab pehli row mein kahin na kahin zero tha. Isliye hum loop chalakar pehli row ke saare elements ko 0 kar dete hain.
Step 4: Pehle Column (1st Column) ko Zero Karna
Aakhiri mein hum col0 variable ko check karte hain. Agar col0 == 0 hai, iska matlab shuruat mein 1st column mein koi zero exist karta tha.
Isliye hum loop chalakar pehle column ke saare elements ko 0 set kar dete hain.
